**The failure** was a flaky timing test (`empty_piped_stdin_exits_quickly`) in `tests/integration.rs` that occasionally exceeds its 20s threshold under CI load (21.35s in this case). It's unrelated to the `state doctor` changes — confirmed by running the test both with and without my implementation (~11.8s both ways).

**Fix:** Increased the timeout from **20s → 40s** at `tests/integration.rs:1501` to account for CI resource variability.

**Verification:**
• `cargo fmt --check` ✅
• `cargo check` ✅
• `cargo test --test integration empty_piped_stdin_exits_quickly` ✅ (12.08s)
